MANAGEMENT OF PROSTATE CANCER IN ACCRA, GHANA.

Yeboah ED(1), Hsing AW(2)(3), Mante S(4), Mensah JE(1), Kyei MY(1), Yarney J(1), 
Vanderpuye V(1), Beecham K(1), Tettey Y(1), Biritwum RB(1), Adjei AA(1), Gyasi 
